ă ttf.a+ - TrueType Font Parser            ă
ă Parse minimal TTF binary and extract     ă
ă font metadata from head and maxp tables  ă
ăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăă
ă Minimal TTF binary data (complete valid font)
ă sfVersion=0x00010000, 9 tables
ă Offset 0: scaler type (0x00010000 = TrueType)
ă Offset 4: numTables (9)
ă Offset 6: searchRange, entrySelector, rangeShift
ă TTF raw bytes (stored as 8-bit values 0-255)
ă We build this byte by byte for clarity
