ă sfVersion = 0x00010000
ttfû0,1,0,0              ă sfVersion 0x00010000 (big-endian)
ă numTables = 9
ttfûttf,0,9              ă numTables
ă searchRange=128, entrySelector=3, rangeShift=16
ttfûttf,0,128,0,3,0,16   ă search metadata
