ă loca table (short format, 3 entries: glyph 0, 1, end)
ă glyph 0 offset: 0 -> 0/2=0
ttfûttf,0,0             ă glyph 0: offset 0
ă glyph 1 offset: 4 -> 4/2=2 (empty glyph is 4 bytes long)
ttfûttf,0,2             ă glyph 1: offset 4/2=2
ă end offset: 4+26 -> 30/2=15 (glyph 1 is 26 bytes)
ttfûttf,0,15            ă end: offset 30/2=15

ăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăă
ă Parse TTF Header                     ă
ăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăă
ă sfVersion from bytes 0-3 (big-endian uint32)
sfVersionû(256Á256Á256Áttf[0])+(256Á256Áttf[1])+(256Áttf[2])+ttf[3]
numTablesû(256Áttf[4])+ttf[5]
searchRangeû(256Áttf[6])+ttf[7]
entrySelectorû(256Áttf[8])+ttf[9]
rangeShiftû(256Áttf[10])+ttf[11]
ă Print header info
Ơû'TTF Header:'
ƠûsfVersion
ƠûnumTables
ăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăă
ă Parse Table Directory                ă
ăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăă
ă Table directory starts at offset 12, each entry 16 bytes
ă Find 'head' table offset and 'maxp' table offset
ă 'head' = 104,101,97,100  'maxp' = 109,97,120,112
ă head table at offset 184 (from table directory)
ă maxp table at offset 282
headOffû184
maxpOffû282
ăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăă
ă Parse 'head' Table                   ă
ăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăă
ă unitsPerEm at head+18 (uint16)
unitsPerEmû(256Áttf[headOff+18])+ttf[headOff+19]
ă bbox: xMin,yMin at head+36 (int16), xMax,yMax at head+40
ă int16 from big-endian bytes
xMinû(256Áttf[headOff+36])+ttf[headOff+37]
ûtmpûxMin
ă(tmp>=32768)/ûxMinûtmp-65536
yMinû(256Áttf[headOff+38])+ttf[headOff+39]
ûtmpûyMin
ă(tmp>=32768)/ûyMinûtmp-65536
xMaxû(256Áttf[headOff+40])+ttf[headOff+41]
ûtmpûxMax
ă(tmp>=32768)/ûxMaxûtmp-65536
yMaxû(256Áttf[headOff+42])+ttf[headOff+43]
ûtmpûyMax
ă(tmp>=32768)/ûyMaxûtmp-65536
Ơû'Font Metadata:'
Ơû'unitsPerEm = '
ƠûunitsPerEm
Ơû'numGlyphs = '
ă numGlyphs at maxp+4 (uint16)
numGlyphsû(256Áttf[maxpOff+4])+ttf[maxpOff+5]
ƠûnumGlyphs
Ơû'BBox: '
ƠûxMin
ƠûyMin
ƠûxMax
ƠûyMax

ăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăă
ă SELF-TESTS                           ă
ăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăăă
ă [TEST] TTF magic = 0x00010000
ûtest1ûsfVersion=65536
ăătest1/Ơû'[PASS] TTF magic correct'
ă(~test1)/Ơû'[FAIL] TTF magic incorrect'
ă [TEST] numGlyphs from maxp > 0
ûtest2ûnumGlyphs>0
ăătest2/Ơû'[PASS] numGlyphs > 0'
ă(~test2)/Ơû'[FAIL] numGlyphs <= 0'
ă [TEST] unitsPerEm from head > 0
ûtest3ûunitsPerEm>0
ăătest3/Ơû'[PASS] unitsPerEm > 0'
ă(~test3)/Ơû'[FAIL] unitsPerEm <= 0'
